<title>nǐ zì jǐ de pú táo yuán yǒu méi yǒu kàn shǒu 迦南1388</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ zì jǐ de pú táo yuán yǒu méi yǒu kàn shǒu, yǐ jīng huāng liáng le hěn jiǔ,
 yuán zhōng de zá cǎo yǐ gāo guò le qiáng tóu, nǐ zài nǎ lǐ tíng liú?
 kuài kuài huí dào yuán zhōng xiū lǐ kàn shǒu, xiàn zài hái shì shí hòu,
 chú qù jīng jí zá cǎo jiǎn qù shí tóu, yī fēn gēng yún yī fēn fēng shōu,
 nǐ zì jǐ de pú táo yuán yī dìng kàn shǒu, zhǔ de shèng líng yǐ wèi nǐ dān yōu,
 nǐ zì jǐ de pú táo yuán yī dìng kàn shǒu, gāo yáng de hūn yàn yǒu yuán zhōng de měi jiǔ.</lyrics>
</song>